commit_message: Report size of each sequence in fasta
Extract top hits from blast alignment

GFF specific feature to sequence

usage: python gffFeatures_to_seq.py <genome.gff> <gff file> <feature> <outputfile>

Create annotation features for introns & flanking

python make_gene_features.py <genome.gff> <upstream> <downstream> <outputfile>
Example: python make_gene_features.py IPGA_gene_1.1.gff.txt 1000 200 updated.gff

Add files via upload

usage: python seqSize_finder.py <genome.fasta> <selected_ids.txt> <ouput_Selected_seq.fasta>
